‚ä¢ evaluate
  given ask‚Üíquestion ‚â° "(shared branch rebase scenario)"
  given ask‚Üítarget-understanding ‚â° "rebase rewrites hashes, safe only for local/unpushed"
  given simulate-student‚Üíanswer ‚â° "(correctly identifies duplicate hash problem, derives rebase-local/merge-shared rule)"
  given simulate-student‚Üíconfidence ‚â° "confident"
  yield correct, misconceptions[], understanding-level

  yield correct ‚â° true
  yield misconceptions ‚â° []
